All in all, I t...Full ReviewVery helpful for planning your day out as well as keeping track of who you have seen. This year, the updates based on weather were very helpful and timely. I didn't spend much time listening to the songs on the app, so I can't comment on that. I also enjoyed their updated social tab. All in all, I think it was incredibly useful for the festival, and I look forward to improvements to it in the future.
